793
00:40:13,567 --> 00:40:17,103
Eh bien, merci, Christina.

794
00:40:19,547 --> 00:40:21,523
- Tu les as ?
- Oui.

795
00:40:21,538 --> 00:40:24,050
- Tiens.
- Merci.

